    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你被困在了一艘死气沉沉的太空飞船中，每一步都令你胆战心惊。你必须探索、求生，并想办法安全返回地球。沉浸在Cosmodread细腻而紧张的气氛中，忘记头戴设备之外的世界。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1256060/extras/700691cc23f6601f752bc5d6485847cf.poster.avif?t=1755506227\" width=614 height=212 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1256060/extras/700691cc23f6601f752bc5d6485847cf.webm?t=1755506227\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1256060/extras/700691cc23f6601f752bc5d6485847cf.mp4?t=1755506227\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >探索</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探寻资源，寻觅归家路。每一次探索，你都将在程序生成的新地图中展开游戏，房间、走道、物品和危机的位置也将随机更改，危险场景也不尽相同。每一扇门的背后，都是一个难以预知的神秘结果。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >生存</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用双手与环境互动。打开房门、抽屉和储物柜，翻看里面的物品。收集基本资源，并制作武器和装备以应对敌人和危险。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >战斗</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >蹲在掩体后方，使用十字弩射杀敌人，或引诱它们进入布好的陷阱。但要记住：弹药是稀缺品！有时候，更好的办法是拿起架子上的一个东西扔出去，引开追杀你的怪物。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1256060/extras/c116b4b535d7335a078a62afc9a73249.poster.avif?t=1755506227\" width=614 height=212 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1256060/extras/c116b4b535d7335a078a62afc9a73249.webm?t=1755506227\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1256060/extras/c116b4b535d7335a078a62afc9a73249.mp4?t=1755506227\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>如果你对Cosmodread感兴趣，不妨了解一下White Door Games的前作<strong>Dreadhalls</strong>。</i></p>",
